"{\n  \"text\": \"A lot of people have problems eating gluten and lactose. And oftentimes this is because of leaky guts. What's going on with our leaky guts is that there's perforation, small holes in our bowels where our food is absorbed, and this food leaks into the circulatory system where it's absorbed through the blood. And this is a much slower, more painful, more inflammatory way of doing things. It's a problem. And you'll first notice this problem, generally speaking, with gluten and lactose because they are huge food molecules. They're ginormous. So when they do go into the blood system, they create a ton of inflammation as they bounce around in there. And this is a place where this is going to lead to other food sensitivities because this is just the beginning of the problem. And we can fix this. This is a problem that is totally curable. You can heal your gut. And a lot of times, you know, we get confused about foods and we think, oh, this is a problem food. Well, no, it's a problem food because of our problem system. So we can fix this, we can heal this, and we should. Eat more fermented foods are good for you. Thanks, Sarah.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" A lot of people have problems eating gluten and lactose.\",\n      \"start\": 0.24,\n      \"end\": 3.84,\n      \"duration\": 3.6,\n      \"confidence\": 0.993,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" A\",\n          \"start\": 0.24,\n          \"end\": 0.4,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.998\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" lot\",\n          \"start\": 0.4,\n          \"end\": 0.56,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" of\",\n          \"start\": 0.56,\n          \"end\": 0.72,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" people\",\n          \"start\": 0.72,\n          \"end\": 0.96,\n    